---
title: Creole Honey Beef Rump & Zesty Veggie Fries with Apple Slaw & Smokey Aioli
description: Kicking us off is this mouth-watering creole seasoned beef rump drizzled in a sweet honey coating and served with a smokey
aioli. The colourful display of roast veggies fries are also bringing their A-game tonight so you best join in the fun too!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
